    "panels": [
      {
        "text": "### Reusing Functions\n\nFunctions are also useful when you have the same chunk of code used in multiple places.\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/157b8c7f3c2c30c9c458126c8ca901f5-reuse-1.png",
        "key": "music-lab-functions-practice-abstract-panel-3b135fec-37b5-421c-a078-8aa602a6b152",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Reusing Functions\n\nYou can use **abstraction** to create a single function that represents this chunk of code...\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/a934152a1d4592df307b73418f82eb48-reuse-2.png",
        "key": "music-lab-functions-practice-reuse-panel-94194e51-0818-461e-a97a-d829f34bac3d",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Reusing Functions\n\nAnd then re-use that function every place the original code appeared\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/89ecdd2d72e97474f6116b9e0e8375c2-reuse-3.png",
        "key": "music-lab-functions-practice-reuse-panel-4e0427a6-39c1-44cc-9553-b64fb5fc48d8",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Reusing Functions\n\nThis makes it easier to keep building your song using these smaller pieces\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/a742a2a8543d3e84044d16569dd036ff-reuse-4.png",
        "key": "music-lab-functions-practice-reuse-panel-918f36ab-1956-40e4-a947-e11812153370",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "Key Takeaway: Use abstraction to notice places where you have the same code in multiple places...\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/dee40cc0aad491d26002e08db021b143-reuse-6.png",
        "key": "music-lab-functions-practice-reuse-panel-f578bb93-a196-4211-b83a-2095d6b1a050",
        "typing": true,
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "... and replace that code with functions that you can re-use in your song\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/e32309c007316f678a24a68ba054b9a9-reuse-7.png",
        "key": "music-lab-functions-practice-reuse-panel-db417716-9e76-4c29-81ab-04ad05d734e2",
        "typing": true,
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "layout": "text-top-left"
      }
    ],
